        "trust_2": "No stimulants",
        "trust_3": "No needles",
        "trust_4": "3rd-party tested",
        "trust_5": "Made in USA",
        "problem_intro_1": "You've been here before. You've tried the calorie counting, the supplements that made you jittery, maybe even priced out those GLP-1 injections everyone's talking about. And every time, the same thing happens — either the results don't stick, the side effects aren't worth it, or you'd need to spend $1,000 a month just to get started.",
        "problem_bold": "You're not failing. The options have been failing you.",
        "problem_intro_2": "The weight management industry has given you two choices, and neither one is great:",
        "problem_card_1_icon": "💊",
        "problem_card_1_title": "Supplements that don't work",
        "problem_card_1_text": "Caffeine and stimulants that drop water weight, spike your heart rate, and leave you right back where you started in 3 weeks.",
        "problem_card_2_icon": "💉",
        "problem_card_2_title": "Injections that cost $1,000+/mo",
        "problem_card_2_text": "GLP-1 shots require a prescription, weekly needles, and come with nausea and GI side effects. And most people regain the weight when they stop.",
        "bridge_text": "What if there was a third option? One that works <em>with</em> your body's natural systems — enhancing the same GLP-1 pathway those injections target — but in a $64 pill instead of a $1,000/month prescription?",
        "bridge_bold": "That's exactly why WLP-1™ exists.",
        "first_cta_heading": "Ready to stop guessing?",
        "first_cta_text": "Join thousands who've already made the switch.",
        "first_cta_button_text": "Try WLP-1™ Risk-Free →",
        "first_cta_button_url": "#offer",
        "first_cta_sub": "Just $64 · No prescription · No needles · Cancel anytime",
        "what_kicker": "What it is",
        "what_heading": "A GLP-1 Boost in a Pill. No Needle Required.",
        "what_text": "WLP-1™ is the first orally bioavailable GLP-1 biomimetic. In plain English: <strong>it helps your body produce more of the same \"fullness hormone\" that GLP-1 injections target.</strong>",
        "benefit_1_icon": "↑",
        "benefit_1_text": "Boosts natural GLP-1 — the hormone that tells your brain you're full",
        "benefit_2_icon": "↓",
        "benefit_2_text": "Reduces ghrelin — the hunger hormone that drives cravings",
        "benefit_3_icon": "🔥",
        "benefit_3_text": "Increases thermogenesis — burn more calories at rest, even without exercise",
        "benefit_4_icon": "✓",
        "benefit_4_text": "No caffeine, no stimulants, no jitters",
        "benefit_5_icon": "✓",
        "benefit_5_text": "Formulated with an expert medical advisory board",
        "benefit_6_icon": "✓",
        "benefit_6_text": "Third-party tested to pharmaceutical-grade standards",
        "proof_kicker": "The proof",
        "proof_heading": "These Aren't Marketing Claims. They're Clinical Trial Results.",
        "proof_intro": "Every ingredient in WLP-1™ has been tested in peer-reviewed, double-blind, placebo-controlled human clinical studies — the gold standard. Here's what they found in people with a BMI of 25+:",
        "stat_1_number": "12%",
        "stat_1_label": "body weight reduction in 10 weeks*",
        "stat_2_number": "321%",
        "stat_2_label": "increase in natural GLP-1 levels*",
        "stat_3_number": "4 lbs",
        "stat_3_label": "lost in the first 4 weeks alone*",
        "stat_4_number": "22%",
        "stat_4_label": "improvement in eating control*",
        "callout_heading": "How does that compare to prescription GLP-1?",
        "callout_bullet_1_icon": "↑",
        "callout_bullet_1": "CQR-300® increased GLP-1 levels by over 300% in 16 weeks",
        "callout_bullet_2_icon": "⚖️",
        "callout_bullet_2": "Comparable to oral semaglutide results in the same trial",
        "callout_bullet_3_icon": "🍽",
        "callout_bullet_3": "Participants reduced daily intake by 500+ calories — through better satiety, not willpower",
        "ingredients_kicker": "What's inside",
        "ingredients_heading": "3 Patented Ingredients. 3 Pathways. Clinically Dosed.",
        "ing_1_name": "CQR-300®",
        "ing_1_benefit": "Boosts GLP-1 & blocks fat absorption",
        "ing_1_stat": "↑ 321% GLP-1",
        "ing_2_name": "IGOB131®",
        "ing_2_benefit": "Resets appetite hormones & cravings",
        "ing_2_stat": "↓ 49% leptin",
        "ing_3_name": "Capsifen®",
        "ing_3_benefit": "Burns more calories at rest",
        "ing_3_stat": "20x absorption",
        "delivery_text": "All powered by <strong>Body Ready™ Tripeptide complex</strong> — a proprietary delivery system that changes how your body absorbs everything above:",
        "delivery_bullet_1_icon": "⚡",
        "delivery_bullet_1": "20x greater bioavailability than standard capsule formulations",
        "delivery_bullet_2_icon": "🛡",
        "delivery_bullet_2": "Nanoemulsion technology protects ingredients through digestion",
        "delivery_bullet_3_icon": "✓",
        "delivery_bullet_3": "The ingredients actually reach your system — that's the difference",
        "review_kicker": "Real people",
        "review_heading": "What People Are Saying After 30–90 Days",
        "review_1_text": "The food noise is just... gone. I used to think about snacking constantly. By week two I realized I'd gone the whole afternoon without even thinking about food. That's never happened to me.",
        "review_1_name": "Sarah M.",
        "review_1_detail": "43, lost 9 lbs in 6 weeks",
        "review_2_text": "I looked into the injections but $1,000 a month? No way. WLP-1 is $64, does what I needed — less hunger, more control — and I don't have to stab myself with a needle every week.",
        "review_2_name": "James R.",
        "review_2_detail": "51, on month 3",
        "review_3_text": "My doctor noticed improved cholesterol numbers at my last checkup. I told her I'd started WLP-1 and she said 'keep doing whatever you're doing.' That was all I needed to hear.",
        "review_3_name": "Diana K.",
        "review_3_detail": "38, on month 2",
        "quiz_heading": "Not sure if WLP-1™ is right for you?",
        "quiz_text": "Take our 2-minute quiz to get a personalized weight management plan and see your projected timeline.",
        "quiz_button_text": "Take the Quiz →",
        "quiz_button_url": "/pages/quiz",
        "quiz_sub": "Free · Takes 2 minutes · Get your personalized results",
        "timeline_kicker": "What to expect",
        "timeline_heading": "Your First 90 Days — Here's What Changes",
        "tl_1_when": "Week 1–2",
        "tl_1_title": "The food noise quiets down",
        "tl_1_text": "Most people notice reduced snacking urges and easier portion control first. Less thinking about food. More energy throughout the day.",
        "tl_2_when": "Week 3–4",
        "tl_2_title": "The scale starts to move",
        "tl_2_text": "Clinical studies showed ~4 lbs lost by week 4. Cravings — especially stress-related ones — continue to decrease. Blood sugar stabilizes.",
        "tl_3_when": "Week 5–8",
        "tl_3_title": "Clothes fit differently",
        "tl_3_text": "Body composition shifts become visible. Waist and hip measurements shrink. Cholesterol and inflammation markers improve.",
        "tl_4_when": "Week 9–12",
        "tl_4_title": "Your new normal",
        "tl_4_text": "Up to 12% body weight reduction at the 10-week mark in clinical trials.* Your appetite, metabolism, and relationship with food have shifted.",
        "steps_kicker": "How it works",
        "steps_heading": "3 Steps. 60 Seconds a Day. That's It.",
        "step_1_title": "Take 2 capsules each morning",
        "step_1_text": "With water. No timing hacks. No complicated cycling.",
        "step_2_title": "Your body does the rest",
        "step_2_text": "GLP-1 goes up. Ghrelin goes down. Thermogenesis kicks in. You eat less without the crash. You burn more without the struggle.",
        "step_3_title": "Results build week over week",
        "step_3_text": "This isn't a spike-and-crash. It's a recalibration. Consistent daily use = compounding metabolic benefits.",
        "final_cta_kicker": "Your plan",
        "final_cta_heading": "Start WLP-1™ Today.<br>Feel the Difference by Week 2.",
        "final_cta_guarantee": "No prescription. No needles. No stimulants. No $1,000/month price tag.<br>Free shipping on subscription plans. Cancel anytime.",
        "final_cta_button_text": "Shop WLP-1™ — $64 →",
        "final_cta_button_url": "/products/wlp-1",
        "faq_kicker": "Common questions",
        "faq_heading": "Still have questions? We get it.",
        "faq_1_q": "How is this different from other supplements?",
        "faq_1_a": "Most supplements rely on caffeine and stimulants — and the results are usually just water weight. WLP-1™ uses three clinically studied, patented ingredients that target your body's actual metabolic pathways: GLP-1 production, appetite hormone regulation, and thermogenesis. No stimulants. No caffeine. No jitters.",
        "faq_2_q": "Do I need a prescription?",
        "faq_2_a": "No. WLP-1™ is a dietary supplement. No prescription or doctor's visit required. That said, we always recommend talking to your healthcare provider before starting any new supplement.",
        "faq_3_q": "Are there side effects?",
        "faq_3_a": "WLP-1™ contains GRAS (Generally Recognized As Safe) ingredients and no stimulants. In clinical studies, ingredients were well-tolerated with no significant adverse effects. Capsifen's nano-beadlet formulation avoids the stomach irritation standard capsaicin can cause.",
        "faq_4_q": "How long until I see results?",
        "faq_4_a": "Most people notice reduced cravings within 1–2 weeks. Clinical studies showed ~4 lbs lost by week 4, with up to 12% body weight reduction by week 10 (BMI 25+). We recommend at least 90 days for best results.",
        "faq_5_q": "Why is it so much cheaper than injections?",
        "faq_5_a": "GLP-1 injections are prescription pharmaceuticals that require doctor visits, insurance authorization, and ongoing dose escalation. WLP-1™ is a dietary supplement made with clinically studied natural ingredients — no prescription, no medical oversight costs, no injection supplies. That's how we deliver GLP-1 support for $64 instead of $1,000+.",
        "faq_6_q": "Can I cancel my subscription?",
        "faq_6_a": "Yes. Cancel anytime from your account dashboard. No hoops, no phone calls.",
        "disclaimer": "*These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. The weight management effects of WLP-1™ ingredients are based on research studies conducted on populations with a BMI of 25+ (overweight). Individual results may vary. Consult your healthcare provider before starting any supplement program. WLP-1™ is a dietary supplement and is not a replacement for any prescribed medication.",
        "sticky_bar_text": "WLP-1™ · <span>$64</span> vs $1,000+/mo injections",
        "sticky_bar_button_text": "Shop Now →",
        "sticky_bar_url": "#offer"
      }
    },
